<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="strchr" id="strchr">strchr</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
语法：
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span><span class="kw3">strchr</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str, <span class="kw4">int</span> ch <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>

strchr() 返回str中第一次出现ch的位置指针，如果没有发现ch返回NULL。
</p>

<p>
